{"tid":1603677,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[請廣傳]新屋嶺受害者S同學公開葵涌警署平面圖同被捕須知！！","createTime":"2019-09-29T17:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T05:26:48.000Z","uid":149328,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"60878c86ce788b3c57a12eab5611393b9c5c9c20","tid":1603677,"uid":149328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:39:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我朋友中大S同學怕popo呢幾日又捉班AP（被捕人士）入葵涌警署<br />\n所以想同大家講返捉咗入去嘅流程<br />\n佢畫嘅手稿：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a3uHTOM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa3uHTOM.jpg&h=2df168f0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n蘋果日報動畫師製作嘅平面圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pXthHHW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpXthHHW.jpg&h=96c732e3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家可以留意附近警署停車場有冇落閘，有就通常係有AP係入面</span><br />\n當日9月1嘅流程係先由警車送到警署<br />\nStep 1:影相，會影哂正面側面，會要求你著返被捕當刻嘅衣著<br />\nStep 2:除低膠索帶手扣，轉咗扣白色有AP number嘅索帶<br />\nStep 3:用金屬採測器scan個身（popo會掀起你件衫，一定要拒絕）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你可以要求由同性警員負責</span></span><br />\nStep 4: popo要填張form比值日官，向值日官報到後就會將你資料寫上白板<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">白板上有你中英全名，歲數，案件主管全名，報到時間同所在位置，怕有人被自殺，就盡量背埋其他AP資料</span></span><br />\nStep 5:落警誡口供，<strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你記得律師電話就話要打比律師，唔記得就睇返警署份律師名冊，冇律師陪同千奇唔好落口供</span></strong></strong><br />\nStep 6:落三世（問你有冇犯罪紀錄、黑社會背景、精神病紀錄、紋身）<br />\n你可以拒絕回答<br />\nStep 7:放低exhibits<br />\nStep 8:將你movement入機<br />\nStep 9:搜屋（可以打比律師要求律師陪同）/搜身（分三級，如果係第三級，即係全裸搜身一定要嘈，會由2名同性警員入去搜身室SEARCH ROOM幫你搜）<br />\nStep 10:入臭格（可以無限次拎毛毯，會有乾同濕紙巾提供）/放你係有蓋停車場繼續坐膠凳（你訓到咪訓，訓唔到咪記低所有細節，出嚟畫返平面圖）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n（1）打電話/去廁所/食飯/入院睇醫生全部AP應有權利佢都會拖你，少則1個鐘，多則10個鐘，所以未急就好嗌定要去<br />\n（2）所有細節（環境佈置、PC number、時間）你要記得好清楚<br />\n（3）律師係到，就記得即時講低你所有要求，律師跟進班popo就會即做</span>"},{"pid":"8b2d58864048b0876b04e3deb872d9d1a2d722f9","tid":1603677,"uid":149328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:40:19.000Z","msg":"重有，所以<span style=\"color: red;\">AP部電話同八達通</span>都一定會沒收<br />\n可以買過部/問朋友借過部<br />\n要完哂成單case（都一年半載）先拎得返"},{"pid":"3e9bc6a3c7fc9fd73cbda2c1664aa52e61b716c9","tid":1603677,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586f5104fe863703afa3ec2791a5915d33e9cc37","tid":1603677,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1469b419c7083a47c5f969056919d391877af477","tid":1603677,"uid":216239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:45:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"775baed0772d71131fb8e05fc2a4d1432f2bbc68","tid":1603677,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:48:42.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d2b7c350f3aaf73ad3a865a44c93bf5c0b955b","tid":1603677,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c757a1bec576aacfa54a4d2dd7f2cc1bf29a066c","tid":1603677,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e807ba3f3eb7489e11a927aa913c41a82d8dc582","tid":1603677,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:58:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04d29c0c0b2c2b7d444a6013be385d682ea691b3","tid":1603677,"uid":68654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:59:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00facb31fceb1b06048ab6031fef2693ff866ab6","tid":1603677,"uid":280136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB